      • Itinerary

        public Itinerary(org.json.JSONObject jsonObject)
        Create a new Itinerary object based on a JSON Object. The JSON Object must contain at least the following values: 
         
 {
     "itinerary_code": "-1",
     "itineraryname": "test",
     "title": "Titolo",
     "description": "Descrizione",
     "beginningDate": "01-01-2000",
     "endingDate": "01-01-2000",
     "reservationDate": "01-01-2000",
     "location": "Location",
     "duration": "00:00:00",
     "repetitions": "1",
     "minParticipants": "0",
     "maxParticipants": "0",
     "fullPrice": "0",
     "reducedPrice": "0"
 }
        Parameters:
        jsonObject - The JSON object from which data will be fetched.
